OL,3,CWarmer weather set to bring 'welcome
OL,4,Cexplosion' of spring colour, RHS says
OL,6,FThe UK could be in for an explosion of
OL,7,Fspring colour over the next two weeks
OL,8,Fas warmer conditions bring flowers
OL,9,Frapidly into bloom, horticultural
OL,10,Fexperts have said.
OL,12,FThe Royal Horticultural Society (RHS)
OL,13,Fis predicting that mild weather,
OL,14,Frising temperatures and some sunshine
OL,15,Fwill lead to colourful displays as
OL,16,Fdaytime highs are forecast to reach
OL,17,Fdouble figures and night-time
OL,18,Ftemperatures stay above 5C.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
