OL,3,CWarmer weather set to bring 'welcome
OL,4,Cexplosion' of spring colour, RHS says
OL,6,F"At RHS Garden Wisley in particular,
OL,7,Fthe lack of a prolonged cold spell in
OL,8,Fthe South which would normally stall
OL,9,Fgrowth means that we are not even out
OL,10,Fof February yet and the hoop daffodils
OL,11,Fon the alpine meadow are already
OL,12,Fstarting to emerge," he said.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,19,F"The camellias are coming through, and
OL,20,Fyou can almost see the magnolia buds
OL,21,Funfurling before your eyes."
